text: Cecily Strong (born February 8, 1984) is an American actress and comedian. She is former a cast member of Saturday Night Live, joining the show in 2012, and left in December 2022. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Chicago Category:Actors from Oak Park, Illinois Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Comedians from Chicago Category:People from Springfield, Illinois
